ese pools is ba=\r\nsed on the balancing of karma/karmaphala sequencing of all beings.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; =\r\n&gt;&gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; The assignment and or=\r\ndering of these pools will constantly undergo churn as one engages in vario=\r\nus new actions and adds them to the pools. Also, as new people enter one&#39;s =\r\nlife, possibilities in terms of karmaphala delivery agents and sequencing m=\r\nay change and hence the pools may be\n re-arranged.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=\r\n=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; *=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=\r\n=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=\r\n=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82=\r\n&nbsp; *=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=\r\n=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=\r\n=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=\r\n=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; As one engages in remedial measures =\r\nsuch as prayers, fasting, donations etc, one may transform one&#39;s nature, ch=\r\nange one&#39;s vulnerabilities or re-arrange one&#39;s dynamics with other beings (=\r\nincluding planets, deities etc, who are the subtle agents of delivery of ka=\r\nrmaphala, who operate through other people who act as physical agents of de=\r\nlivery!). The karma pools may be re-arranged as a result. Some undesirable =\r\nkarmas may be downgraded to a lower pool or pushed down in order within the=\r\n same pool. Or, some desirable karmas may be upgraded to a higher pool or p=\r\nushed up in order within the same pool.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=\r\n=82&nbsp;When someone curses or blesses one,\n with sufficient mental force =\r\nbehind it (this is the key), the same thing can happen. It is all about re-=\r\narranging karmas between the karmik pools. Every action by one, or even peo=\r\nple around one, has the potential to re-arrange one&#39;s karmik pools. A karma=\r\n about to give karmaphala may be postponed or a karma that was not to give =\r\nkarmaphala anytime soon may be advanced sooner.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=E2=\r\n=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; However, remember that the remedial mea=\r\nsure has to be as intense as the karma that it is trying to manipulate. You=\r\n can move a small rock with small force, but you need a large force to move=\r\n a big rock or a hill.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt;=\r\n &gt;&gt; &lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; If there is no negative karma in one&#39;s pool tha=\r\nt can give a specific result, nobody can make one experience that result, n=\r\no matter what ritual one does. However, even great souls have a lot of nega=\r\ntive karmas in their optional pool and even evil people have a lot\n of posi=\r\ntive karmas in their optional pool, and hence powerful remedies, curses and=\r\n blessings can often make some difference.&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=83=E2=80=9A=\r\n=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; This point is well illustrated by the &quot;Guru C=\r\nharitra&quot; story Digamber ji referred in his point (3).&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=\r\n=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; *=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=\r\n=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nb=\r\nsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=\r\n=82&nbsp; *=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=\r\n=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=\r\n=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;=C3=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp; *&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; =C3=\r\n=83=E2=80=9A=C3=82&nbsp;&lt;BR&gt;&gt; &gt;&gt; If one thinks that one can escape=\r\n the fruits of one&#39;s actions, one is mistakened. God is not like us human b=\r\neings, who may show favoritism towards those who praise them or bribe them.=\r\n T